Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... They're all bills! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! It's about time you got up.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.22,0:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.08,0:00:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you looking at these again? \NLook, forget about them already, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.99,0:00:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know, I'll just tear them up! \NThat way you'll be able to move on.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.52,0:00:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.55,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, you say... {???????? no clue at all}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.07,0:00:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.76,0:00:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because I didn't know any better...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.08,0:01:04.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,About a week ago, a salesman from\Na securities company visited the Warumon Lab,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.12,0:01:07.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and ZakoBee, who was at home at the time, \Nfell for his smooth sales pitch
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.51,0:01:10.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and ended up buying a ton of stock.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.51,0:01:17.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was told it would double in a week, and thinking\Nhe'd surprise his master, ZakoBee kept it a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.43,0:01:21.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But those stocks were actually from\Na company on the verge of bankruptcy!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.65,0:01:24.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, before the week was even up, \Nthe company collapsed,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.87,0:01:28.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the stock certificates weren't even worth the paper they were printed on.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.59,0:01:32.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I don't usually get many lines, \Nso I figured I'd narrate for a bit in this episode.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.87,0:01:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault... Because of me, \NMaster ended up like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.75,0:01:40.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,I've gotta fix this somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.96,0:01:45.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,How do I get him back \Nto his usual shining, cool self?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shining...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shining... Like his shiny head? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not like that! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.21,0:01:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Master, why not try\Nbuilding a mech or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.68,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You look coolest \Nwhen you're building machines!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.12,0:02:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A mech? I can't think of anything to build...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.81,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything's fine! \NAs long as it's anti-TwinBee.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee? TwinBee...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, {\i1}these{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! It pisses me off.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.08,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's build the Super Deluxe Soul Changer \NI designed and give the TwinBee team a hard time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.52,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That one? Yeah... \Nmaybe I should make that...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.66,0:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I will...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.25,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Build it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, ZakoBee...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Will building it get our money back?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.11,0:02:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{waruwaru}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even if I do build it...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to cheer up, Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.70,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to never forget your dream—\Nto be recognized as the world's greatest scientist!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.67,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's greatest...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.92,0:03:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NThe greatest scientist in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.82,0:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NI {\i1}am{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}the greatest scientist in the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This setback is nothing! {lit: how can I lose to something like this}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.28,0:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, ZakoBee! Let's get started\Non the development of a new mech!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye! Roger that!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Deluxe Soul Changer, was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, first we need materials! \NGo buy them!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no money...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.32,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's greatest scientist can't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You're number one, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Number one, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.19,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.74,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NI'm the greatest scientist in the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, ZakoBee! Let's get to work \Ndeveloping that new mech!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate anti-TwinBee weapon!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Super Deluxe Soul Changer! \NAll right! Let's buy the mat...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel's on her way home from school.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.38,0:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner's gonna be curry... \NYes, seafood curry!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.08,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And where'd you come from, kitty?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute! I wanna pet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything to lure it over? {play with it to make it come closer}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.05,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? ZakoBee?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and use this.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.05,0:06:14.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh... Due to budget constraints, even this design's\N a compromise, and I'm not sure she'd even want it. {meaning that usually it'd be a ray gun or something and making this device look like a cat teaser is silly}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,But now's my chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.88,0:06:21.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,Though I feel kinda bad using it on Pastel...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Neat that you've got it with you. Can I?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't touch it there!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, hold it by the handle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, kitty, how about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And now here. No, this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.55,0:06:44.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault Master lost everything...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,So I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.35,0:06:52.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah, Pastel! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.42,0:07:20.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why can I see myself from the outside?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.42,0:07:25.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Then... what am I? Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew. Looks like it worked. \NAh, Pastel, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.34,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.87,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! \NWhat's this cat freaking out about?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Did you sneak in from outside?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, you flea condo?! Get out!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Whose cat is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a noisy thing...\NIs it hungry or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm kinda hungry myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking Pastel so long? \NCan't she hurry up and cook something?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's at the lab?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm listening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Pastel over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, she's not.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.24,0:08:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's usually in the kitchen\Nmaking dinner at this time of the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.20,0:08:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing! She's not, \Nso I thought she might be there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.84,0:08:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's not at the lab either, \Nwhere the heck is she this late?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.35,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting worried. \NI'll go check outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, please do.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.52,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel? Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.74,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if my radar picks her up.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.05,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pastel's right next to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.70,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If the radar is to be believed, \Nshe's on the other side of this bush.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel! I've come to pick you up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.21,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.60,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pastel! Just cook something already, \Nit doesn't matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.18,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel, everyone's hungry! \NHurry up and prepare some dinner.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.90,0:09:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Your own stomach is growling too! \NStart cooking something already!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.79,0:10:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel! What are you doing?! \NThat's no way for a lady to behave herself!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Help me with Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.46,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is it about Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.03,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, \Neating that squid raw?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.87,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's sneaky! Prepare dinner properly,\Ndon't just hog it all to yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't hiss at me! \NGimme that squid...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.57,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel! What's gotten into you? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You bastard... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.18,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.71,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's the matter with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying holed up in her room like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.15,0:11:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to go to bed hungry because of her... {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.48,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something\Nto make her feel bad, perhaps?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's the matter with you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? W-What are you up to? \NWe're siblings, remember? {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you know this is all way too sudden! {????????? only hear "ikinari" = suddenly}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it's deterring me or anything... {??????? kinda hear "of course I wouldn't say that kind of line"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.67,0:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She just fell asleep. \NWhat on earth is wrong with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.89,0:11:43.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah, why did this have to happen? \NBefore I knew it, I found myself in a cat's body.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.25,0:11:49.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,It seems like my words aren't getting through at all, \Nso what can I do to get them to understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.98,0:11:53.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,Sleep... Sleepy...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.13,0:11:57.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,No! I can't sleep! Not until I think up \Na plan for what to do next!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.96,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up working\Nthrough the night again...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, it's almost done.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?\NPastel's not cooking today?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Doc,\Nit's even worse than it looks.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.98,0:12:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think someone \Ndid something to upset Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.34,0:12:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't go looking at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.04,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why was Pastel sleeping in your bed?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.24,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.78,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd just abandon \Nher chores for no reason!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.31,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You people seriously \Ncan't understand the reason?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.19,0:12:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.77,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... maybe we've been\Nrelying on Pastel too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.07,0:13:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still just a middle school girl. \NShe'd want to hang out with friends after school too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.62,0:13:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But we just ignored that \Nand kept tying her down with housework.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.43,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys didn't even realize that? \NThat's pretty dumb! So near-sighted!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.00,0:13:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Pastel. From now on, \Nwe'll all take turns doing the chores.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The fried eggs are ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.30,0:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Pastel, eat it while it's hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.43,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong, Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't waste food like that, Pastel...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.06,0:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not nice at all, P-Pastel. \NYou should apologize... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.29,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.11,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck's wrong with you, you brat?! {???? maybe "now you've done it, idiot"}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! Dr. Cinnamon snapped!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what do we do? \NI've never seen him like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, take Pastel and get to school! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Pastel's not safe here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What, really? Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're off!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.58,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, we made it in time! \NSeriously, what happened to you, Pastel...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up, Pastel.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel? Pa—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch! Time for lunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My lunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.48,0:15:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's definitely wrong with her. \NThis is {\i1}not{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but what are we\Nsupposed to learn from this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we even looking for?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything at this point.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't help at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}is not our Pastel, at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What if... she's a fake? {double}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.16,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake? Oh, don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.52,0:16:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit talking and start looking!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't take it out on me! Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, TwinBee?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, let me go for a sec.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this, what do you think it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.45,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? We don't even have a cat, \Nso why a cat teaser?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Light! Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, TwinBee...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.88,0:16:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.77,0:16:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Why am I seeing \Nmy own body in front of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with these huge hands?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I... not me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.96,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean... \NLight, did we switch bodies?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.25,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.99,0:16:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I TwinBee?! \NTwinBee is supposed to be...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like, round, flying around like “whoosh”...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm TwinBee!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's it! That's what caused it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What, the cat teaser?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How would something like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.21,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I had no idea it was this fragile!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're stronger than you look...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee? What is that cat?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been hanging \N around here since yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.47,0:17:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pestering me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But this cat sure is weird. \NThe way it meows is almost like it's trying to talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... could that cat be Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.12,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right...\NThat explains her weird behavior!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! The cat and Pastel switched bodies!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.73,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... this has to be Dr. Warumon's doing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do we do? This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.63,0:18:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The swapping device is broken. \NIf we get attacked now, we're done for!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.46,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right! \NThese bodies are way too different to handle.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.12,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, operation complete. Over!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! That was smooth work!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.66,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do we do after that? \NWhat should we do next? Over!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.32,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,According to your plan, what's the next step? \NHow do we defeat TwinBee? Over!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.01,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me! Answer me! Answer me! {/hello}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.89,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... there wasn't really a plan after this...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.28,0:18:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Master! Over! Over!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.64,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Master? Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.19,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! Light! You should be able to go faster!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.76,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push it! \NThis is my first time flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.92,0:19:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, even if we beg him, \Nwill Dr. Warumon turn us back?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.66,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious. But that's a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, can't you fix it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.19,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Most of the parts have totally disintegrated. {/are completely crushed}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.95,0:19:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't repair it, and I don't even\Nknow how it was originally built.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.70,0:19:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do we change back?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.75,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to ask the one who made it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee-bee! So that means...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to plead with Dr. Warumon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.72,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee... Will he even agree to help us?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with it all... {??? nandattenda bakayaro? what the hell idiot}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.62,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened, \Nbut cheer up, okay, Waru? {-chan}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk... I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.61,0:20:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.22,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of living like this anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, is that...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your favorite, right? I'd know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.52,0:20:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.06,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you're here?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.11,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I left a note saying\N“Don't look for me,” though...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.78,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.94,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've a reason why we\N{\i1}absolutely{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}must find you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.05,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally found you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.68,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am! More snacks. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.38,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just ignore us! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.87,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So how's it feel being switched? Fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.01,0:21:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet it is! {/Yeah, real funny - probs?}\NWe're in serious trouble here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't a laughing matter!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.01,0:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came all the way here \Njust to tell me that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.43,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, actually... we came to ask you \Nto turn us back to how we were!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! Please, Dr. Warumon!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{P-Please...}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.48,0:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I did this to mess with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.22,0:21:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I change you back now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer forever! {lit: I want you to be in this trouble for the rest of your lives}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.01,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And why come to me anyway, huh? \NWhat about Cinnamon?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.60,0:21:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your own genius scientist\NDr. Cinnamon at home, so ask him!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.32,0:21:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.07,0:22:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That cat teaser is broken, \Nand Dr. Cinnamon can't fix it, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.96,0:22:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Well, that checks out. \NOf course he can't do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.46,0:22:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Dr. Warumon! \NTurn us back!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.69,0:22:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We admit it, you're a genius scientist!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.94,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you finally admit it. \NThen there's only one thing I have to say to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.80,0:22:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.13,0:22:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.89,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.95,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided I'm done building machines.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.02,0:22:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, it all started to feel pointless.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.67,0:22:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The neverending battle of wits with Cinnamon, \Nbuilding anti-TwinBee mechas...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.61,0:22:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to feel ridiculous \Nfor getting so worked up over it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.56,0:22:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Dr. Warumon!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.23,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What was my life even about up to now?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.45,0:23:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, I'll take that bottle. {that she offered}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.77,0:23:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.95,0:23:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right here...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.12,0:23:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Your chat was taking too long, \Nso I drank it. Whoopsies!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.00,0:23:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! That was my special, \Nmy absolute favorite...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.56,0:23:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was real good!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn bet it was!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was premium sake, 800 yen a bottle!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.03,0:23:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I only get to drink once a year! And yet you... You...!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.95,0:23:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, that's it! \NI'll never forgive you for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.90,0:23:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, it's just some booze!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.81,0:23:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always hated that attitude of yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! There's no way I'm losing to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.03,0:23:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Cinnamon! \NI'll make you eat your words!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.20,0:23:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Dr. Warumon! \NDoes that mean you'll build mechas again?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.43,0:23:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Now we can turn back to how we were!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.00,0:23:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.27,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get started on the design, ZakoBee!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! {waru}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.27,0:23:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the lab, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.70,0:24:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.97,0:24:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.26,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stay like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.84,0:24:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and turn us back!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.56,0:24:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn us back!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.77,0:24:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, no need to rush. \NThere's plenty more.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:29.49,0:24:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Seafood cookies... \Nare they really that good? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.87,0:24:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But why aren't you using your hands, Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.67,0:24:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who cares?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.93,0:24:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's theme: “Who would you\Nlike to switch places with?” Cast:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.02,0:25:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee—Mayumi “I'd switch with Kishino Yukimasa
Dialogue: 10,0:25:00.14,0:25:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and go home to apologize to\Nmy wife for everything I've done.” Tanaka! {same as in ep2, kishino yukimasa is the voice of warumon, fans were shortening his name as a joke to K野Y正 = K[ishi]no Y(read as "wai")[ki]masa - together it gives us "keino waimasa"}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.04,0:25:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel—Hekiru “I'd like to be reborn as the\Nblue sky and watch different eras pass by.” Shiina.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.92,0:25:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,WinBee—Kumiko \N“My dog—he's got it easy.” Nishihara.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.77,0:25:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint and GwinBee—Miki “A refined, classy,\Nbeautiful French woman in her early 20s.” Ito.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.09,0:25:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Cinnamon—Kazumi “Gandhi” Tanaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.61,0:25:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka—Mariko “Couldn't think of anything...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.24,0:25:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'd like to quietly become \Na grain of wheat.” Kokuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:39.60,0:25:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,ZakoBee—Yusuke “Ken Takakura.” Numata. {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ken_Takakura}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:44.40,0:25:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stock salesman—Koichi “Doraemon, \Nhe can make any dream come true.” Nagano. {did he even have any lines? lol}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.41,0:25:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bar owner—Wakana “I'd switch with\NTetsuya Kumakawa and dance freely.” Yamazaki. {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tetsuya_Kumakawa}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.99,0:26:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Warumon—Yukimasa “It's a secret.” Kishino.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.67,0:26:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Light—Kappei “Miki Ito,\Nbut as a beast-man.” Yamaguchi. {???? maybe jinjuu = beast in human form, maybe chinju =  rare (or peculiar) animal? idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.94,0:26:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That concludes our program!
